{"tid":1588843,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"去左食反送中小店中大伏！3","createTime":"2019-09-23T04:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T09:18:16.000Z","uid":13361,"like":72,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3136d50ab27d08fca6ea09c9199103388c6673e0","tid":1588843,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHFi3oD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHFi3oD.png&h=29276eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2Jvd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2Jvd5.png&h=ed57774f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫左鄰居漢堡和雞扒漢堡跟set配雙色著條和汽水<br />\n讚好facebook送caffe latte一杯 有去讚好但暴徒係唔需要你地施捨既 飲可樂算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dB2ENRG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdB2ENRG.jpg&h=bd9c182b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄰居漢堡-味道同價格都屌打burgeroom同附近既burgerman<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />juicy牛肉漢堡扒加上焦香既罐頭菠蘿 配以煙肉芝士中和甜味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有秘製醬汁 巧巧味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個bell皮都有烘乾 呢啲先係真正既burger呀<br />\n雙色薯條都值得一讚 啲蕃薯條同薯條連皮同有薯味 全部都外脆內軟 應該係用新鮮蕃薯同薯仔整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />$18好抵加 屌打mos加廿幾蚊先有既薯條 <br />\n不過份量又係好多 又係食到好飽<br />\n<br />\n香草雞扒漢堡-朋友話雞扒好大塊但有啲鞋 不過香草味濃 整體味道都唔錯 薯條好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想食漢堡既話 晚市六點開始有8-10安士安格斯牛西冷餐 $148包薯條 沙律同飲品 我以前食過 都幾抵屌<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZaX9qMJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZaX9qMJ.png&h=e92123a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過會得薯條無蕃薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊懲罰啲罷工偷懶既暴徒 一齊食到佢地抽泣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄰居<br />\r\n    <br />\r\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0jAa700~ufMj9Ag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0jAa700~ufMj9Ag&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=16b510e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0jAa700~ufMj9Ag</a><br />\r\n地址: 長沙灣元州街162-188號天悅廣場地下A8號舖<br />\r\n電話: 37020958<br />\r\n<br />\n附近仲有蛋香烘焙 賣雞蛋仔夾餅 同枝裝自家製既飲品 仲有串燒小店 吉寸 價錢平服務又好而且用心製作 不過一向都多街坊幫襯 想食最好訂位 同樣非常高汁 想食甜品仲有請暴徒食西米露既甜一刻 店內仲有暴徒figure<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Ni1gVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ni1gVY.jpg&h=19a50e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蛋香烘焙<br />\r\n    <br />\r\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0ndu900~ufMj9Ag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0ndu900~ufMj9Ag&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=9d44a820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0ndu900~ufMj9Ag</a><br />\r\n地址: 深水埗營盤街138號安寧大廈地下A舖<br />\r\n<br />\n吉寸<br />\r\n    <br />\r\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS00JC800~ufMj9Ag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS00JC800~ufMj9Ag&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=b05444b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS00JC800~ufMj9Ag</a><br />\r\n地址: 深水埗營盤街132號地下<br />\r\n電話: 61691928<br />\r\n<br />\n甜一刻<br />\r\n    <br />\r\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0zCM100~ufMj9Ag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0zCM100~ufMj9Ag&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=b0554bc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0zCM100~ufMj9Ag</a><br />\r\n地址: 長沙灣福榮街218號美居中心62號舖地下<br />\r\n電話: 35686757"},{"pid":"f2e2135bc4a1b4011e8a712c0da2211208c8fe98","tid":1